Package: kanban-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: kanban
Description: GitHub Kanban workflow CLI tool
 Kanban is a CLI tool for applying Kanban methodology to GitHub organizations.
 It manages labels, workflows, and issue tracking across multiple repositories
 with a single configuration file.
 .
 Features:
  - Label management and synchronization across repositories
  - Local SQLite database for offline queries and metrics
  - Terminal-based kanban board view
  - Comprehensive metrics with bottleneck detection
  - Config-driven with YAML presets
 .
 XDG-compliant paths:
  - Config: ~/.config/kanban/config.yaml
  - Data: ~/.local/share/kanban/kanban.db
